_sText:
- 64 CT and 3 T spawnpoints
- nice breakable floors with physboxes
- 14 traps with 2 automatic pop-up turrets
- cool soundtrack
- some custom textures and skybox

This is my first deathrun map. I think it is not a very hard, may be good for medium skill players.
All who will fall in a lava will be teleport into noob box.
The map will start to break in 120 seconds after round start.
You also must type net_maxfilesize 30 (or greater) in your server.cfg file (or server console) for play on this map.
